HEADWORD: Denier
<hw>De*ni"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who denies;
<as>as, a <ex>denier</ex> of a fact, or of the faith, or of
Christ</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

